-----Original Message-----
From: Pat Raedy [mailto:pr@satisfied-mind.com]

Posted To: Copyright
Conversation: Notification of Claimed Infringement
Subject: Notification of Claimed Infringement

A domain hosted with ThePlanet.com has copied my site. 
http://www.saynotocabletv.com/google/ is a copy of my site,
